text: The Embraer Emb-312 Tucano is a Brazilian single-turboprop military aircraft. Its cockpit has two seats. The Royal Air Force use Tucano built under licence by Shorts. More than 600 examples were built. Its main competitor is the Swiss Pilatus PC-9. Category:Brazilian military aircraft 312 Category:Royal Air Force aircraft
title: Embraer Emb-312 Tucano
